snippet.title: Inazuma Eleven GO - Time for Kickoff! (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Inazuma Eleven GO: Light and Inazuma Eleven GO: Shadow has kicked off on Nintendo 3DS. Get a taste of the action with the launch trailer.

Official site: 
https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-3DS/Inazuma-Eleven-GO-Light-883636.html
